Run:

helm upgrade --install bscf <chart-path> -n cnf -f local-values_26A-2u-t1.yaml

Replace <chart-path> with your actual chart directory.


---

Then Verify

Run:

oc get po -w

BIP pods should now:

create successfully

attach networks correctly

start containers



